and we hope it inspires you as a

00:33:31.986 --> 00:33:34.876 A:middle
starting point to many new cool

00:33:34.876 --> 00:33:37.056 A:middle
video effects to create in your

00:33:37.056 --> 00:33:37.776 A:middle
applications.

